N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 46.3 - Services

State Regulations

Services will be provided through State-approved
accredited veterinarians licensed and registered with the Education Department, or either employees of the Department of Agriculture and Markets or United

States Department of Agriculture. A record of vaccinations will be provided the
herd owner or his agent. Notes
